            Founded in 1907, Bessemer Trust Company is a privately owned investment firm that offers hedge funds and private equity and real estate investment options. The firm provides estate and tax planning, family wealth stewardship, and philanthropic and insurance advisory services. It evaluates estate planning techniques and considers asset allocations that balance the risks of concentrated holding products. Bessemer Trust Company works in association with insurers to develop custom loss prevention measures. Its additional products include letters of credit, secured loans and checking accounts. The firm offers wire transfer, currency conversion and personal bill payment services. It assesses personal travel options and club and resort travel programs, as well as provides 24-hour concierge services.
          






















